/span></div><div>I'd seen just a 2 minute clip of Adam Savage talking about empathy, and sought out the full video, here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rMtcxaj02mg

From that I extracted 3 minutes that focuses on his advice for enduring through these hostile times we now face in society where empathy is now weaponized.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jCjgzAI.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Most people who are successful, owe it to opportunities of kindness that came their way... and they accepted that kindness. Someone empathetic, who saw potential in someone and gave them a shot. Often times, even against the odds. Like, they could've simply passed and it wouldn't have made a difference in their lives. But they CHOSE to make a difference in someone else's life.

That's the power of empathy.

The far-right doesn't understand that. They take, take, take, and never give back.

I want to point out one more thing about empathy.

It is directly connected to generosity. The giving of something to someone else without expectations of getting the same or more in return.

The survival instinct is greed. The more you have, the better off you tend to be. And there's usually collateral damage with excessive greed. Too many people have forgotten this. Our "modern society" has celebrated greed. And now... it's coming back to bite us hard on the ass. And it hurts. We're infected. And we need to inoculate. Badly. This whole anti-vax movement that RFK Jr. joined in and is now weaponizing in government is representative of the OPPOSITE of what's needed. We can't move forward until these people are no longer in office, ruining lives.

WE NEED TO BRING BACK KINDESS and EMPATHY. Hold them as qualities to strive for and admire. Not to be reviled. Society can't thrive and be healthy on hate, division, animosity, vindictiveness, lying, grievance peddling, and the grifting of the gullible and weak. That's the world we're in now, because of Donald Trump and the Republican Party who complicitly enabled all of this. ALL OF IT.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/IDQU1q1</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[cytherians]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>&quot;It's not as popular as their pretending it is&quot;.... Love it, so fucking true!!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/KMIP24A</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wdSatPC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/KMIP24A</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[DumpingSh1tandBeingKind2]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Chicago, the most dangerous city!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/fvqNWFE</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Um6Lf8n.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/fvqNWFE</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[countervail247365]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>He totally drinks Baileys from a shoe.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/qKbUhlf</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/L6CbFTb.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/qKbUhlf</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[MayMyEnemiesLiveLong]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>&quot;They suck, so you don't have to.&quot;</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/YRkkONj</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XFPO543.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/YRkkO